1. She can translate this letter. 2. Who can help me? 3. She can go to the shop and
buy milk. 4. My brother cannot speak Spanish. 5. My sister cannot cook. 6. Can you
run fast? 7. I cannot drink cold milk. 8. He can't tell the truth, can he? 9. Nobody
can run faster than a lion. 10. Can you see that girl with a black bag? 11. Couid you
come earlier? 12. Last year I could not go to Barcelona. 13. Could you tell me where
I can buy strawberry? 14. Could you tell me where the underground is? IS. I can't
work so much. 16. He cannot drive a car, can he?
